window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Go deeper with the Ravenhood Legacy in this second installment of the sizzling, darkly seductive, internationally bestselling series spin-off. Here, at last and in his own words, is Tyler's story, never before published.</b></p> <p><i>Once upon a time...</i></p> <p>There lived an ambitious boy determined to become a man before his time. And a woman and battered soldier who recognized the scars that marred his soul—scars that mirrored her own.</p> <p>Determined to help shape the warrior within him, it was their inexplicable bond that would forever alter his heart. And the loss of that love that would redefine his destiny.</p> <p>After all, nothing has ever been fair in love and war.</p> <p><i>Narrated in duet style.</i></p>"; 
